channel.title: GDG DevFest CDO 2014
channel.description: GDG DevFest is an annual developer conference offered by the Google Developer Groups

item.title: DevFest is back!
item.description:
We’re very excited for this year’s biggest developer conference offered by our local Google communities. Yes, GDG DevFest CDO is back!

This year, our friends from Capitol University is very kind to host our event.

It’s gonna be bigger!

  • Attendance: we’re expecting over 300 attendees
  • Topic: more than 28 hours of pure Google technologies
  • Date: 29th of November
  • Venue: Capitol University Theatre

Hope to see you soon!

Like us on Facebook, follow on Twitter, add to circles in Google+.

item.title: Apply to become a delegate
item.description:
We will be closing the Online Application on November 24, 2014 at exactly 12 midnight and will start to send confirmation emails on the same day. Don’t miss this chance to attend this year’s GDG DevFest CDO! Apply now!

If you have any inquiries, don’t hesitate to contact us at gdgcdo@gmail.com.
